entry.tran: 无（特殊）技能的;未经专门训练的
entry.def: People who are unskilled do not have any special training for a job.

example.ex: He went to Paris in search of work as an unskilled labourer...
example.tran: 他没有任何劳动技能就到巴黎找起了工作。

example.ex: Most of those who left the province to work abroad were unskilled.
example.tran: 那些离开该省出国打工的人大部分都未经专门训练。

entry.tran: 无需(特殊)技能的；不需专门训练的
entry.def: Unskilled work does not require any special training.

example.ex: In the US, minorities and immigrants have generally gone into low-paid, unskilled jobs.
example.tran: 在美国，少数族裔和移民一般都会从事低薪水、无需特殊技能的工作。
